{"id":111,"date":"2020-08-27T12:00:21","date_gmt":"2020-08-27T12:00:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/?page_id=111"},"modified":"2024-09-25T19:30:58","modified_gmt":"2024-09-25T19:30:58","slug":"markets","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/company\/markets\/","title":{"rendered":"Markets"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"111\" class=\"elementor elementor-111\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31cffbe9 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"31cffbe9\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-524b4009 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"524b4009\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e7f49d0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1e7f49d0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span class=\"smallheader blue\">Diesel-Hydrogen Assist Technology (D-HAT\u2122)<\/span> Diesel <span class=\"green\">Improved<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-77873d77 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"77873d77\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-639c7cdc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"639c7cdc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In today&#8217;s global economy, diesel remains the most effective, practical power source for long-haul transportation (trucking and marine), fueling heavy equipment, and power generation. Heavy loads require high torque that electric vehicles just can&#8217;t deliver. That&#8217;s why 90% of all goods around the globe continue to be moved by diesel. There simply isn&#8217;t an effective, efficient, or economically feasible alternative at this time.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-37c3c9c2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"37c3c9c2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;video&quot;,&quot;background_video_link&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.youtube.com\\\/watch?v=aKLmHVpvaLU&quot;,&quot;background_play_on_mobile&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-video-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-video-embed\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-542e5ca3 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"542e5ca3\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-650a7c65 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"650a7c65\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Diesel's <span class=\"green\">Challenges<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4527f876 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4527f876\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-158b6a89 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"158b6a89\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3db1c53f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3db1c53f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67616a94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"67616a94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Carbon <span class=\"green\">Emissions<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-653cfaf3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counter\" data-id=\"653cfaf3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"counter.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter-number-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-prefix\">Up To <\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number\" data-duration=\"1000\" data-to-value=\"35\" data-from-value=\"0\" data-delimiter=\",\">0<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-suffix\">%<\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4b3150a6 e-con-full elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4b3150a6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29a3b65a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"29a3b65a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Diesel exhaust accounts for <span class=\"green bold\">35% of global greenhouse gas emissions<\/span> that contribute to climate change. Every gallon of diesel burned creates 22.2 pounds of CO2. In older engines, it also means productivity losses every week due to Diesel Particulate Filter (DPF) regeneration.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7587bbe0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7587bbe0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5dc51f0c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5dc51f0c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-77f14802 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"77f14802\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Fuel <span class=\"green\">Inefficiencies<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af3596c elementor-widget elementor-widget-counter\" data-id=\"af3596c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"counter.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter-number-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-prefix\">Up To <\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number\" data-duration=\"1000\" data-to-value=\"70\" data-from-value=\"0\" data-delimiter=\",\">0<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-suffix\">%<\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4eafa646 e-con-full elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4eafa646\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-26d74ae6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"26d74ae6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Typical diesel combustion efficiency is <span class=\"green bold\">only 70%<\/span>, wasting energy every time fuel combusts, resulting in less-than optimum performance in both MPG and torque. The remaining, partially burned fuel becomes black soot (diesel particulates) and nitrous oxide (NOx), which negatively affect air quality, producing green-house gases, smog and acid rain.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e799c49 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e799c49\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18a0ea9a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"18a0ea9a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c873d37 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4c873d37\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Engine <span class=\"green\">Wear and Tear<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-244a3558 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counter\" data-id=\"244a3558\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"counter.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter-number-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-prefix\">Up To <\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number\" data-duration=\"1000\" data-to-value=\"18\" data-from-value=\"0\" data-delimiter=\",\">0<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-suffix\">%<\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f4260ed e-con-full elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3f4260ed\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0170c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b0170c4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Wear and tear generated by partially burned fuel deposits can <span class=\"green bold\">reduce power output and fuel efficiency of a diesel engine by 18% or greater<\/span> over a truck&#8217;s first 250,000 miles.\u00a0 Inefficient combustion creates carbon buildup in the engine, increasing the need for more frequent oil, filter, and emissions system replacements that drive up maintenance costs and erode profits.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-61251a35 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"61251a35\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f00a27b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f00a27b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-333fef0d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"333fef0d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Industry <span class=\"green\">Solutions<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ec7c32 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2ec7c32\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>D-HAT\u2122 devices can be modified and scaled to meet a broad range of commercial and industrial applications, including trucks, buses, heavy equipment, marine vessels, and more.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-630de31e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"630de31e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-144a3f6f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"144a3f6f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c03236e e-con-full solutionbox e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c03236e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-02a898e solutionimg elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"02a898e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/train.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1727\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/train.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/train-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3cf7e8c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3cf7e8c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-780e663 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"780e663\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Rail<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b5b645 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6b5b645\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The rail industry, like many off-road diesel-powered heavy industries, is facing pressure to cut down emissions. Rail companies need to act quickly to reduce their carbon footprints, especially with older engines, or consider replacing them with new models models.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62da78a e-con-full solutionbox e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"62da78a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05f42f0 solutionimg elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"05f42f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/marine.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1728\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/marine.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/marine-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e5fd5ba e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e5fd5ba\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-079699a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"079699a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Marine<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b12b6aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b12b6aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Over 90,000 heavy marine vessels burn the dirtiest bunker fuels on the market. HOD Tec generators can help to eliminate the scrubbers and filters while cleaning up the dirty exhaust.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67363de e-con-full solutionbox e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"67363de\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-656ece7 solutionimg elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"656ece7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/gen-set.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1726\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/gen-set.jpg 600w, https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/gen-set-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc739f9 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"bc739f9\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6814e58 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6814e58\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Generators <\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-529dc70 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"529dc70\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Diesel generators release up to 50 times more pollutants and NOx compared to large combustion plants. The addition of D-HAT\u2122 can significantly reduce harmful diesel exhaust emissions while also reducing fuel costs.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e4d4bf8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e4d4bf8\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0b4133 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b0b4133\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df52499 e-con-full solutionbox e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"df52499\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-10f1c94 solutionimg elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"10f1c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/trucks.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1725\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/trucks.jpg 600w, h