ading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Transition to <span class=\"green\">More Effective<\/span> Diesel Operations With Hydrogen On Demand<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18a372d1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"18a372d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Practically any large diesel combustion engine that runs on diesel fuel can use a D-HAT\u2122 device to save money and meet consumer and regulatory demands for clean power. Our systems will contribute to operational excellence and increase profitability by making your diesel engines run cleaner longer and more efficiently.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-548428f4 greenbutton elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"548428f4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/hodtec.com\/technology\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">About D-HAT\u2122 Technology<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-abb5814 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"abb5814\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d8e6748 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1d8e6748\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;motion_fx_motion_fx_s